<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Koivusaari</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-10-14 17:49:17</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>This item is indeed dropped in the Temple of Droga.  It is dropped by Chief Rukgus.  The chief has 3 drops on him, the most common one being the Rukgus's Sticker (piercer), the second and fairly rare drop is the Essence of Dol (1hb MNK only), the finaly drop is the Idol of the Thorned (ac10, str7, sta10) this item does in fact go in the range slot and is all/all.  Myself and another Necromancer camped this item for about a week and we saw 2 of them drop in that time.  The price for these items run around 50k on Prexus.  I would not suggest you sell it though since it is the best ranged item in the game thus far.  If you were to sell it though, i suggest you ask for something you will never get rid of, or a very large amount of platinum.<BR>
<BR>
Hope this information clears things up for you =)</font></td></tr></table>
